cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the system aspects of development of applied programming interfaces in Software-Defined Networking (SDN), which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also covers issues related to programming automation, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses metadata representation in SDN API, which is related to data centers (cs.DC).
